title: Ambient Design ArtRage v2.5.19 Multilingual Retail Incl. Keymake
description:
Here is something pretty useful for graphic artists. ArtRage is nice and easy to use painting application, which imitates old skool style of painting (brush, pencil, sketching?). If you have a graphic tablet maybe, possibilities are endless. Who knows, maybe is new Van Gogh inside of you.. :D

Description:

ArtRage 2 is our simple, stylish, and fun painting package that gives you realistic tools in an easy to use interface. Paint with oils, sketch with pencils, chalks, and crayons, sprinkle metallic glitter on your paintings and more. ArtRage 2 also supports multiple transparent layers, PSD files, layer blend modes, and a variety of other features for the professional artist.
